We import legal products from different countries on customer's request. The cost of importing is not fixed. We also import parcel that is sent from any foreign country to u. For importing this kind of parcel parcel we need the airBill number of that parcel.
It take smore time to import than export. we normally import your desired product within 72* hours. Sometimes it takes weeks to import. Thats why before importing we give our customer an estimated date.
**Usually we import products using DHL,COE and DPEX
